{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"56553-today-i-am","title":"Ano Kaya Ako Ngayon?","description":"Ano kaya si Maria ngayon? Isang eksplorador, astronaut o alagad ng sining?","language":"Filipino","langCode":"fil","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kaye Sucgang"],"illustrators":["Sandhya Prabhat"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/56553-today-i-am"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/524542/size3/c273da52c55bd7e5d79cd98401ab3ab2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/524542/size6/c273da52c55bd7e5d79cd98401ab3ab2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79839/size6/1851e5b94ad11e38a3b2cde61db55123.jpg","text":"Ngayon, ako ay isang astronaut.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79842/size6/ec46fba085b7c0b7520393b6e2ac5595.jpg","text":"Tingnan mo kung gaano ako kataas tumalon sa ibabaw ng buwan.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79846/size6/064618d423802e81431a50ec9c574156.jpg","text":"Ngayon ako ay isang eskultor.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79848/size6/9027bf58d6fde98a2bbcd06b7956240d.jpg","text":"Maghanda ka, ang aking buwaya at dinosaur ay gutom na.\nRawrr!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79849/size6/bf9cc0b14bae2957869e160f1f35a525.jpg","text":"Ngayon, ako ay isang manlalaro ng cricket.\n*Ang cricket ay isang kilalang laro sa India na gumagamit ng bat at bola. Nilalaro ito sa pagitan ng dalawang koponan ng labing-isang manlalaro.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79850/size6/c177b8f8619d94ff6120879fcd3645a2.jpg","text":"Ako na ang titira. At...tanggal ka na!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79851/size6/f8f6ce4db1412cc86f58c0f3f83a1592.jpg","text":"Ngayon, ako ay isang botaniko.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/80013/size6/38eddd9f67af4042a5c6c59f27ccca51.jpg","text":"Nakatuklas ako ng bagong halaman. Ipapangalan ko ito sa akin.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79853/size6/c60ae14f325211467333dd90f2dc3d5e.jpg","text":"Ngayon, ako ay isang tambolero.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79854/size6/90ef5f7c7a184ec7371c2c1a6d410830.jpg","text":"Dhushh! Tsshh! Sa bilis ng paghampas ng aking mga panambol, hindi mo na ito makikita.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79855/size6/0296786590d7aa884ec45c3905f0245b.jpg","text":"Marami talaga akong gustong maging.\nAno naman kaya ako bukas?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":115}}